metadata.name: CHITORI X LUSS
metadata.description:
"People hate people who are reluctant to share their love. But what if you have too much to share?”  

八神 千鳥(Yagami Chitori) is an icon of the pop culture. An artist, a diva, an idol to be followed and a notorious easy lover to be hated….Her history of romance is phenomenal so is her talent in performance art.  

At the end she still enjoys her way ongoing: be true to herself and every little hubby puppets she crouched and consumed…this is what life should be lived! 

 C’est la vie~~~

 “Just SATISFIES THE THIRST OF MY LUSS!”
